<p><b>What are asset management interview questions?</b> 1. Can you describe your experience in managing IT assets? This question allows candidates to provide an overview of their experience and expertise in IT asset management. Look for candidates who have a strong understanding of asset lifecycle management, inventory control, and software licensing.</p>
